## Schema

### Required

- `id` (String) ID of the notification channel to look up.

### Read-Only

- `created_at` (String) Creation timestamp.
- `name` (String) Channel name.
- `org_id` (String) Org ID.
- `type` (String) Channel type discriminator (e.g., `slack`).
- `updated_at` (String) Last-update timestamp.
